Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:10.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm looking back at the old photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:12.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:21.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,This is a picture of when we were still\Nin lessons before our debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:24.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,Zekken is different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:27.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,There were so many of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:30.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,Now there are six of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:33.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:34.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:37.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,It was when we all went to the\Nwaterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.61,0:00:40.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,It was a hit song of "Kuroi Hitsuji".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.61,0:00:44.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,It was hard, but it's still in my\Nmemory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.61,0:00:48.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,I can only show you this for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:53.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,When we were performing at Fuji-Q\NHighland,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:57.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,I woke up early in the morning and took\Na picture on the roller coaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:01.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,Everyone was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:04.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,I looked at the camera and hid my\Nforehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:07.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's so surreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.07,0:01:14.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,But I was able to ride a jet coaster in\NNaoki at 7 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:16.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,It was a great awakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:18.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:21.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:23.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please subscribe to my channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:25.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please check the latest video on my\Nchannel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:27.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:36.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,This is the picture after the last live\Nof Kiyakizaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:41.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,I took a picture with Takahiro-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:43.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,I like it very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,I miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:52.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,This is a picture of the award ceremony\Nwhen I received the Nagane Dresser\NAward.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:57.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,I remember everyone wearing glasses and\Ngiving a speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,I remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,I miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:10.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,This is a picture of us when we happened\Nto find ourselves and were happy when we\Nvisited Lawson.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:20.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was happy to collaborate with the shop\Nthat we decorated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:23.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,I miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:25.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,This is with Hono-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:29.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,This is when we had the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,This is my favorite photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,The one that I miss more than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:35.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,When we did the music video.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:37.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,When we all campfired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,This is the photo I took with Kira-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:48.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Kira-chan, who is a little older than\Nme, has a lot of hair on her face, so\NI'm a little worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:54.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Kira-chan's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:59.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Kira-chan's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:05.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Kira-chan's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:11.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Kira-chan's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:16.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Kira-chan's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:20.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Kira-chan's hair is not long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:24.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Kira-chan's hair is not long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:29.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,She have a lot of thick hair, so I'm\Nworried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:34.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,She have a lot of thick hair, so I'm\Nworried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:39.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Really, I'm worried about her hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:44.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please subscribe to my channel and\Nfollow me on Twitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:53.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,When we spent the day together at the\NKiyaki House,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:57.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,we stayed there for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:59.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,We cooked and ate together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,We jumped into the pool together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:04.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's nostalgic. I like this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:10.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's a great memory that we played "Sui-\NChu-Fu-Kyo-Ao" in the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:25.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Sui-Chu-Fu-Kyo-Ao"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:27.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for a very scary\Nperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'll close the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:32.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:34.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,When I think back,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:37.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there is an eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:41.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,I wanted to change someone's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:45.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to be able to change\Nsomeone's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:47.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,But the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:49.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:51.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's fine if it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:53.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best with 1 million\Nsubscribers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:58.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to be a necessary existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:03.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want people to feel lonely without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:06.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,I've never worked this hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:24.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to be a captain who can be\Nrecognized by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:28.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please support me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:36.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was worried because it was my first\Nexperience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:41.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,I had the image that the captain would\Nlead the team in the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:48.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,I thought, "I can't be the captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:51.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's a pitiful love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:55.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,I think I have a duty to take\Nresponsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:58.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,I can't say it because I think it's not\Nthe position to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:06:59.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:04.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to change so that I can say that\Nit is the position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:09.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to change, but I can't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:20.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,What gave me confidence was the members\Nwho accepted me as I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:23.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I'm Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:25.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm glad Sugaya is the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:28.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm glad Yuka is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I'm Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:33.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I'm Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I'm Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I could go this far\Nwithout her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:40.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,She's watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,I think I've grown up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:51.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,I think I've gotten used to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:54.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,which is a little different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:57.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,I wanted to run away many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,I felt like I was going to be crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:06.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:10.74,ASS,,0,0,0,,*Hololive, it's no good. The heroine has\Nleft the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:13.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,*Even if the heroine is gone, the one\Nwho is coming back home is not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:16.16,ASS,,0,0,0,,*We are standing here to make you\Nrealize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:18.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,*You're just like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:20.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,*We'll be waiting for you, my heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,*My heart is finally at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:26.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,*I'll be with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,*Wherever you are, we're right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:32.22,ASS,,0,0,0,,*Whatever happens, we will always be\Nwith you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm no longer here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will be safe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:43.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,As long as you are by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will never be lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:55.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:57.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will always be here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:59.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will never let go
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:10.78,ASS,,0,0,0,,I am proud to be the captain of this\Ngroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:15.88,ASS,,0,0,0,,I am proud to be the captain of this\Ngroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:14.88,ASS,,0,0,0,,I am proud to be the captain of this\Ngroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.88,ASS,,0,0,0,,I am proud to be the captain of this\Ngroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:34.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,Everyone, thank you for coming to\NSakurazaka46's tour final concert today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:41.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,And thank you so much for holding such a\Nwonderful graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:55.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for making time to\Ncome to the venue during your busy\Nschedule
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:11:02.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,and for watching over us during the live\Nbroadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:07.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to be able to spend this\Nday with my beloved Team Sakurazaka
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:12.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,at the Tokyo Dome, which was my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:19.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take this opportunity to\Nlook back on the past 7 years
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:30.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I joined the team in 2015, and in 2016,\NI debuted as Kiyakizaka46 in Silent\NMajority.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:38.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Looking back, my idol life was full of\Nups and downs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:47.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I think it was a turning point in my\Nlife to be appointed as a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:48.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:53.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was collaborating with my favorite\Nmembers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,It was very complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:07.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,It was very difficult to put together an\Nunbalanced group.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:13.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I felt I was not worthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:17.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,But at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:28.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,There were many members who were in\Ntheir teens, so we all worked hard, but\Nthere were days when things didn't go\Nthe way we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:43.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,At that time, as the captain, I was\Ntrying to do my best to be the bridge\Nconnecting everyone in the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:46.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:56.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,It was hard to convey the image of the\Ngroup that I love
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:07.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,Even though I was prepared for it, I was\Nshocked when I was ignored
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:15.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,It was hard to believe in others
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:17.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,I felt it in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:20.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,I had to lie to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:25.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,It was a time when it was difficult to\Nlaugh from the bottom of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.95,ASS,,0,0,0,,But at that time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:39.95,ASS,,0,0,0,,It was a real relief that everyone who\Nsupported me was there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:46.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,I received a lot of messages of support\Nfrom all over the world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:54.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was really happy to be able to perform\Nlive and perform on various stages
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:14:02.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,and to be able to accept and look\Nforward to my inexperienced self.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:09.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to become a person who can\Nrespond to those feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:17.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to become a person who can be\Nlooked forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:22.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for giving me a chance to move\Nforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:38.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,I am proud of my life that I was able to\Nsing many famous songs written by\NYasushi Akimoto with my favorite\Nmembers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:54.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,Of course, I would like to thank all the\Npeople who have supported me in many\Nways,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,my beloved members,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:05.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,and my family who have always been by my\Nside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:13.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,I am very grateful that I was able to\Nrun this far thanks to the support of so\Nmany people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:17.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:29.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,Since I became a member of Sakurazaka46,\NI've been able to talk about how the\Nmembers' smiles have increased a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:46.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thanks to everyone, my heart has become\Nlighter, and I've been able to laugh a\Nlot as a member, regardless of my\Nposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:16:01.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,I've been fighting with everyone who has\Nbeen with me for so long, and I've\Nbecome a cute junior who adores me as I\Nam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:07.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's very sad to say goodbye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:18.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:40.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,I think Sakura 46, which I love so much,\Nhas grown and become stronger than\Nbefore in the past two years thanks to\Neveryone's support.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:45.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,And everyone is doing their best to move\Nforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:52.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm always full of reliable members who\Nare always doing their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:17:02.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to convey the charm of SAKURAZAKA\Nto more and more people from the bottom\Nof my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:14.22,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to seeing what kind\Nof girls will come to the group that I'm\Nso proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:17.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to seeing SAKURAZAKA\Nfrom now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:21.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,I would be happy if you could support\Nus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:27.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,And my favorite Keyakizaka46 and my\Nfavorite Sakurazaka46
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:36.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,Each of them has their own charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:39.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's not about which one is good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:48.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,I would be happy if you could respect\Neach of them and accept their charms and\Nlove them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:53.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:14.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will do my best so that I can meet you\Nagain, and I will never forget this\Nexperience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:21.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to embrace all the fun and\Npainful things and move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:29.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,I look forward to your continued support\Nfor Sakura Asaka 46 and Yuka Sugai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:31.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:42.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:45.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:48.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:49.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,You are so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:50.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that you like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I didn't mean to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I didn't mean to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:07.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,Actually, I wrote a letter to each of\Nthe members with my feelings for Yuka-\Nsan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:09.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,You wrote a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:11.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:12.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:14.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm about to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:15.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,From Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:17.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,Can I go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:18.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:19.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:23.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,First of all, congratulations on your\Ngraduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:24.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:26.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's my first time meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:31.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,I had a lot of anxiety about whether I\Nwould be accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:36.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,At that time, Mr. Sugai welcomed me with\Nthe best smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:38.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was very relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:45.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was personally depressed when I met\NAsaka Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:50.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,At that time, Mr. Sugai sent me a\Nmessage and said kind words to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:52.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:20:05.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,There were a lot of things, but when I\Nthink about it, I was able to receive\Nthe message that I should do my best,\Nand I was able to do my best positively.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:07.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:11.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm very, very lonely about Mr. Sugai's\Ngraduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:18.78,ASS,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad that Mr. Sugai's feelings\Nand words are still with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:40.78,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will always be in this group, and I\Nwill always have your feelings in my\Nheart, so I think I can do my best to\Ncherish those feelings in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:42.78,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:46.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to give a lot of treasures to the\Ngroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:48.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:50.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will treasure it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work for about 7\Nyears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will support you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:58.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:21:02.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,You are the best captain in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:03.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:06.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:17.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:20.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:22.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Can I hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:23.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:24.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:26.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy! Thank you for accepting\Nme!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:35.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:37.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ah, Hikarin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:41.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka-san, congratulations on your\Ngraduation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:42.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:50.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka-san was the first senior that we\Nmet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:56.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,On the day of the performance, we were\Nso nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:22:00.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,But you came to see us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:04.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,And the first thing you said to us was
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:07.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Thank you for coming to Keyakizaka."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:13.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Since I was assigned to Keyakizaka,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:18.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I felt like my heart was dancing."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:20.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,"On the other hand,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:25.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I wonder if there are fans who would be\Nhappy to join me."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:27.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I was worried about that."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:30.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Yuuka-san, in the words of 'Thank\Nyou',"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.25,0:22:32.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,"replied to me."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:34.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:41.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to be able to feel such\Nwarmth from you, Yuka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:51.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,I thought that I would definitely grow\Nmore in this group and become a\Nnecessary member.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:23:01.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,Now, I think that I only have\NSakurazaka, so everything related to her\Nis important and precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.42,0:23:04.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yuka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:12.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,This time, I will be a member who can\Nhold hands with my new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.59,0:23:19.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for taking care of\Nme in Keyakizaka and Sakurazaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:23.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,And I look forward to working with you\Nforever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:25.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,Endo Hikari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:27.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:29.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.71,0:23:34.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm watching over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:35.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.71,0:23:36.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:37.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.71,0:23:38.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.71,0:23:40.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.71,0:23:42.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.71,0:23:43.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.39,0:23:49.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka-san, congratulations on your\Ngraduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.39,0:23:50.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.39,0:23:55.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for being here today,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.39,0:23:58.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,leading the group as the captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.39,0:24:02.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,in the midst of such unimaginable\Nstruggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.39,0:24:04.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.39,0:24:08.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,When we first met, we promised to stand\Ntogether at the Tokyo Dome,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.39,0:24:12.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,and we wanted to perform the opening\Nsong together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.39,0:24:15.84,ASS,,0,0,0,,So we decided to perform the opening\Nsong together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.84,0:24:20.84,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for both of your\Npromises.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.84,0:24:22.84,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.84,0:24:29.84,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka-san, you always support people\Naround you with a lot of kindness and\Nlove.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.84,0:24:34.84,ASS,,0,0,0,,You always say to people around you, "I\Nwant to repay you."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.84,0:24:42.84,ASS,,0,0,0,,I have received so many things from\NYuka-san that I want to repay her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.84,0:24:44.77,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for leading me so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.77,0:24:53.77,ASS,,0,0,0,,I would like to do my best in the future\Nso that I can give my all to the group\N"SAKURAZAKA".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.77,0:24:55.77,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.77,0:24:57.77,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.77,0:24:59.77,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.77,0:25:10.77,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.77,0:25:11.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.55,0:25:18.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka-san, congratulations on your\Ngraduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.55,0:25:21.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.55,0:25:25.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka-san, I like your smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.55,0:25:27.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.55,0:25:33.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,The moment I met you, you said, "Thank\Nyou for coming to Keyakizaka."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.55,0:25:40.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was saved by the words, "You can stay\Nhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.34,0:25:45.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,For me, Yuka-san is a person who gives\Nme courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.34,0:25:52.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,She told me that she likes the part of\Nme that I don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.34,0:25:59.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,She always watches my performances and\Ntells me that she likes them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.34,0:26:05.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,I've always been worried about my\Nperformance,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.34,0:26:09.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,but Yuka-san always tells me that she\Nlikes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.18,0:26:17.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,Like magic, Yuka-san always tells me\Nthat I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.18,0:26:25.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,She always encourages me to practice\Nmore and improve myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.18,0:26:37.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to follow Yuka-san\Nforever.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.69,0:26:42.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka-san is a person I can't stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.69,0:26:50.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka-san, no matter how big a dream you\Nhave, you can definitely make it come\Ntrue.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.69,0:26:53.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,I really think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.69,0:27:00.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm lonely, but I want to send you a lot\Nof love.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.69,0:27:04.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.69,0:27:07.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.69,0:27:09.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.69,0:27:12.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.69,0:27:14.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.69,0:27:25.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.68,0:27:29.68,ASS,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your graduation,\NSugai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.68,0:27:30.68,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.68,0:27:33.68,ASS,,0,0,0,,Sugai-san is equal to everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.68,0:27:36.68,ASS,,0,0,0,,and always smiles like the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.68,0:27:38.68,ASS,,0,0,0,,which was the support of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.68,0:27:40.68,ASS,,0,0,0,,He kindly guided us,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.68,0:27:43.68,ASS,,0,0,0,,who were confused about which way to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.68,0:27:48.68,ASS,,0,0,0,,and I learned the greatness of the\Ncaptain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.68,0:27:50.68,ASS,,0,0,0,,During this tour,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.68,0:27:53.68,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was able to see the performance of\N"MIC Drop"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.68,0:27:56.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,During this tour, I was able to see the\Nperformance of "MIC Drop"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.66,0:28:00.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was able to see the performance of\N"MIC Drop"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.66,0:28:05.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was able to see the performance of\N"MIC Drop"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.66,0:28:11.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will continue to support you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.66,0:28:13.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.66,0:28:15.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.66,0:28:17.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.66,0:28:28.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.83,0:28:38.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Congratulations on your graduation,\NSugai-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.83,0:28:46.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I didn't feel it during the rehearsal\Nyesterday, but I felt it as soon as the\Nlive started."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.83,0:28:50.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I really didn't want you to come\Ntoday."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.83,0:28:53.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I didn't want it to start."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.83,0:28:58.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,"But I'm so happy to see you so\Nbeautiful like this."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.08,0:29:02.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I still remember the first day I met\Nyou."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.08,0:29:06.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I came all the way here just because I\Nlove you."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.08,0:29:10.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I was worried that I might be a burden\Nto you."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.08,0:29:15.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,"You listened to my unstoppable self-\Nintroduction with a smile."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.08,0:29:22.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I became an idol because you have\Nalways protected the group."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.67,0:29:29.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much for letting me meet\Nsuch wonderful members."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.67,0:29:36.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Please continue to be happier than\Nanyone else with your smile like the\Nsun."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.67,0:29:38.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Thank you very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.67,0:29:40.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.93,0:29:53.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.93,0:29:55.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.93,0:29:57.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yui-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.93,0:29:59.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,To Sugai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.93,0:30:04.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,You gave us infinite love every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.93,0:30:10.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,You always have to think about the group\Nand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.93,0:30:18.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,You look at each other deeply and notice\Nhow small the change of feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.93,0:30:20.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.46,0:30:24.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for supporting the group for a\Nlong time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.46,0:30:29.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for protecting us for a long\Ntime.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.46,0:30:37.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,I met an idol, and now I'm on stage like\Nthis.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.46,0:30:41.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,My idol life has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.46,0:30:43.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.46,0:30:45.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.46,0:30:48.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,My idol life has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.69,0:30:57.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm really happy that Sugai-san was in\Nthe best group to be the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.69,0:31:01.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your graduation.\NPlease be happy forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.69,0:31:03.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.33,0:31:16.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.93,0:31:22.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your graduation,\NYuka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.73,0:31:23.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.73,0:31:29.43,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka-san has always been so kind and\Ncute since the day we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.43,0:31:34.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,As a member of the group, as a person, I\Nreally respect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.83,0:31:38.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka-san, who is always thinking about\Npeople and the group more than herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.83,0:31:41.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,and Yuka-san, who prioritizes and acts\Non behalf of the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.20,0:31:46.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be of help to Yuka-san as\Nmuch as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.20,0:31:57.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't do that, and sometimes I\Nwas worried about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.20,0:32:04.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,However, she was always kind to me, and\NI really liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.20,0:32:10.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to keep up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.20,0:32:12.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.20,0:32:13.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.20,0:32:14.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.20,0:32:25.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.11,0:32:29.09,ASS,,0,0,0,,Riria and Riria are looking at Riria\Nwith tears in their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.09,0:32:31.09,ASS,,0,0,0,,Riria!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.79,0:32:33.79,ASS,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.79,0:32:34.95,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.95,0:32:39.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,When I see you, when you just joined the\Ngroup,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.35,0:32:44.47,ASS,,0,0,0,,I remember the first time I saw you in\Nthe lesson room.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.47,0:32:48.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,At that time, you were very nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.19,0:32:55.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,But you were smiling and talking to me\Nwith a bright smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.59,0:32:55.79,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.79,0:33:01.79,ASS,,0,0,0,,Since then, I have always been grateful\Nfor everyone's equal and kind treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.79,0:33:09.79,ASS,,0,0,0,,And as a captain, I think there were a\Nlot of scenes where I had to speak on\Nbehalf of the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.79,0:33:16.79,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was always full of respect when I saw\Nyou standing in the front and talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.79,0:33:19.79,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.79,0:33:24.79,ASS,,0,0,0,,I wish you a lot of happiness after\Ngraduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.79,0:33:27.79,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.03,0:33:50.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.03,0:33:51.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Hiro-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.03,0:33:52.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.03,0:33:53.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.03,0:33:54.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.03,0:33:57.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your graduation,\NSugai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.03,0:33:58.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.03,0:34:02.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,The two and a half years I spent with\NSugai-san went by so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.03,0:34:04.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,It wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.03,0:34:09.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,I still have a lot to tell you, and I\Nwanted to spoil you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.03,0:34:14.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to stay with me for a long,\Nlong time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.03,0:34:16.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to stay with me for a long,\Nlong time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.61,0:34:21.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,But no matter how long I can stay with\Nyou,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.61,0:34:25.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,I don't think it was enough when I said\Ngoodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.61,0:34:30.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,I have to tell myself that the goodbye\Nthat will come someday
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.61,0:34:33.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,just came at the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.61,0:34:37.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's so painful and I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.61,0:34:41.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's how much you mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.97,0:34:46.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,My everyday joy was Sugai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.97,0:34:52.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,I thought I could meet cute Sugai-san,\Nso I came here every day excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.97,0:34:59.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,Even when I was about to fall down, I\Nwas able to raise my face to see Sugai-\Nsan.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.97,0:35:03.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your reason to do your\Nbest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.97,0:35:07.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your dreamy every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.94,0:35:10.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want you to be the happiest person in\Nthe world.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.94,0:35:12.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,I really love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.94,0:35:14.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.94,0:35:15.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.94,0:35:22.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.94,0:35:26.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.65,0:35:40.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,"To Yukkawa-san, thank you for your hard\Nwork for about 7 years. When I'm with\NYukkawa-san, my heart is at ease and it\Nwarms me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.65,0:35:45.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,When Yukkawa-san told me that she was\Ngoing to graduate, it was when we were\Neating together.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.65,0:35:53.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,Since that day, I've been thinking about\NYukkawa-san every day, and there were\Ndays when I was lonely and anxious and\Nsometimes cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.65,0:35:56.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's how important it is for me to be\Nin a group."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.06,0:36:01.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Honestly, I was very lonely and a\Nlittle anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.06,0:36:09.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,But I learned from Yukkawa-san's back,\Nwho showed me and continued to be strong\Nwhile struggling, and I will do my best\Nto do what I can do."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.06,0:36:13.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I'm really glad Yukkawa-san is the\Ncaptain."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.06,0:36:18.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Because Yukkawa-san was the captain,\Nthis group has now."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.06,0:36:24.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Because Yukkawa-san was the captain,\Nthis group has now."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.94,0:36:28.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I was really happy to be able to work\Nwith Yukkawa-san in this group."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.94,0:36:32.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Congratulations on your graduation. I\Nlove you forever."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.94,0:36:34.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.94,0:36:37.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I'm rooting for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.94,0:36:39.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Let's meet anytime."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.94,0:36:41.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.96,0:36:49.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.56,0:36:56.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your graduation,\NSugai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.96,0:36:57.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.96,0:37:01.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,The day has finally come for you to say\Nthis to Sugai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.96,0:37:08.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,I know you must be feeling really\Nlonely, but your feelings of gratitude\Nare much bigger than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.96,0:37:12.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,Sugai-san always takes the lead in the\Ngroup,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.96,0:37:16.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,and even when things get tough, you\Nalways have a kind smile on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.00,0:37:23.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was able to work with peace of mind\Nbecause of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.00,0:37:28.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for always supporting and\Nprotecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.00,0:37:33.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm really happy to be able to work with\Nyou as a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.00,0:37:36.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work for 7\Nyears.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.00,0:37:42.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,I hope you can continue to spend your\Ndays full of smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.00,0:37:44.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.50,0:37:47.50,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.27,0:37:52.27,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm watching you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.27,0:37:58.27,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.27,0:38:03.27,ASS,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your graduation,\NYuka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.27,0:38:04.27,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.27,0:38:08.27,ASS,,0,0,0,,When I was a trainee and announced that\NI was disbanded,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.27,0:38:11.27,ASS,,0,0,0,,you welcomed me very warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.27,0:38:13.27,ASS,,0,0,0,,When I cried at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.27,0:38:16.27,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka-san said, "It's okay to take your\Ntime."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.27,0:38:18.27,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was very happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.27,0:38:18.98,ASS,,0,0,0,,I still feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.98,0:38:21.98,ASS,,0,0,0,,I remember it vividly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.98,0:38:31.98,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking away our anxiety\Nwith the words and voices we were\Nnervous about.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.98,0:38:37.98,ASS,,0,0,0,,And I'm so grateful that Yuka-san said\Nshe wanted to stand with us at the Tokyo\NDome.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.98,0:38:45.98,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm so grateful that we're able to make\Nit happen now, and we're doing it in\Nsuch a blessed environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.54,0:38:54.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love and admire Yuka-san, who is\Nalways beautiful, strong, and has a kind\Nsmile.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.54,0:38:58.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad that Yuka-san is the\Ncaptain of the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.54,0:39:02.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for supporting the\Ngroup for 7 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.54,0:39:04.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,And thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.54,0:39:17.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.90,0:39:30.90,ASS,,0,0,0,,To Yuka-san, first of all, thank you for\Nyour hard work for the past 7 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.90,0:39:31.90,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.90,0:39:38.90,ASS,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard it is, I want to\Nfollow Yuka-san who is standing with a\Nstrong chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.90,0:39:45.90,ASS,,0,0,0,,There have been many times when I\Nthought it would be okay if the captain\Nsaid it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.90,0:39:49.90,ASS,,0,0,0,,but my heart, which was about to break,\Nwas shaken many times by Yuka-san's\Nwords.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.90,0:39:54.90,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was able to come this far thanks to\NYuka-san's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.90,0:40:01.90,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for making the group\Nand bringing me to the Tokyo Dome as\NSakurazaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.90,0:40:06.90,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for showing me such a\Nwonderful view.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.90,0:40:12.90,ASS,,0,0,0,,I think Yuka-san's warm personality is\Nmost evident in her smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.37,0:40:19.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,I hope her life from now on will be\Nfilled with smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.37,0:40:21.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.37,0:40:23.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.37,0:40:25.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.37,0:40:29.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.37,0:40:36.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,To Yuka, thank you so much for the past\N7 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.37,0:40:39.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,And really, really, thank you for\Neverything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.00,0:40:48.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,Even though there are many difficulties\Nin the job of an idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.00,0:40:54.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,there were many thoughts and worries\Nthat only Yuka could understand in the\Nposition of the group captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.00,0:40:57.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I can't help you at all\Neven though I'm close in age.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.00,0:41:00.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being the captain all the\Ntime.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.00,0:41:05.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,I think from the bottom of my heart that\Nit was really good that Yuka was the\Ncaptain of this group.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.00,0:41:10.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka has been working hard and showing\Nme how hard she works,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.00,0:41:12.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,and I've done my best so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.10,0:41:22.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,When I was having a hard time and I was\Nabout to quit, Yuka always found my good\Npoints and praised me, so I was saved a\Nlot and I was able to continue so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.10,0:41:32.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,When I joined the 4th single for the\Nfirst time, she congratulated me the\Nmost, and I really can't forget the\Nwords she said at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.10,0:41:37.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's really fun to be with Yuka, and I\Nwant to be with her more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.10,0:41:42.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm really lonely to graduate, but I've\Ndone my best so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.11,0:41:45.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please take care of yourself from now\Non.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.11,0:41:49.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka's smile when she's eating delicious\Nfood is the cutest and I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.11,0:41:52.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,Don't hold back and eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.11,0:41:56.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,And thank you for bringing us to the\NTokyo Dome again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.11,0:41:59.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to be a wonderful person\Nlike Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.64,0:42:02.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best! Please continue to\Nsupport me! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.64,0:42:04.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.76,0:42:09.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.76,0:42:11.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,Let's go eat again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.76,0:42:13.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.76,0:42:14.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.76,0:42:18.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.76,0:42:22.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work for 107\Nyears.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.76,0:42:23.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.76,0:42:27.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was still a student when I joined the\Ncompany,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.76,0:42:32.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,so I wasn't used to the new environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.76,0:42:34.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.18,0:42:37.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,She took me to the city of Tokyo for the\Nfirst time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.18,0:42:42.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,She said, "I'll be your sister."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.18,0:42:49.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was relieved and relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.18,0:42:55.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,I remember that I felt like I had a\Nfamily in the Kanto region.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.18,0:43:03.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,My sister was a captain and a pillar of\Nthe group.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.00,0:43:10.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she had a lot of emotions that\NI couldn't measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.00,0:43:14.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,No matter what the situation is, she's\Nso kind and warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.00,0:43:18.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,I really loved Yuka, who wrapped me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.00,0:43:25.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,From now on, as an older sister, but not\Nas a member.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.00,0:43:29.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk to you about a lot of\Nthings at a closer distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.00,0:43:31.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.42,0:43:33.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.42,0:43:35.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.42,0:43:37.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.36,0:43:44.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.36,0:43:54.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka, you've worked hard for 7 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.36,0:43:55.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.36,0:44:00.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's been 7 years since we met, but\Nyou're still as young as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.36,0:44:02.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,Your smile is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.36,0:44:03.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.36,0:44:05.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,There are some parts that are missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.36,0:44:07.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love such pure Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.36,0:44:08.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,As a captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.94,0:44:14.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,You protected the group and listened to\Neach member's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.18,0:44:23.90,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've had a lot of hard times,\Nand I think you've been able to get\Nstronger because you've been watching it\Nby your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.90,0:44:33.22,ASS,,0,0,0,,So I want you to keep in touch with me\Nas a friend, and we can go out for a\Nmeal and talk about things that have\Nnothing to do with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.22,0:44:37.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,I hope that will support each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.58,0:44:39.58,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.58,0:44:41.58,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Let's go eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.49,0:44:48.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.49,0:44:58.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.49,0:45:01.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work for about 7\Nyears.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.49,0:45:02.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.49,0:45:09.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to be here today at the Tokyo\NDome, where Yuka has always wished to\Nstand again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.49,0:45:16.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,There are many days when I can laugh\Nnow, but there are many days when I\Ncan't laugh no matter how hard I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.72,0:45:25.72,ASS,,0,0,0,,No matter what the situation is, Yuka is\Ntrying to protect the members and the\Nfans.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.72,0:45:33.72,ASS,,0,0,0,,I clearly remember Yuka lying down while\Nholding a notebook in one hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.72,0:45:35.72,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.72,0:45:43.72,ASS,,0,0,0,,It may be unfair to say this now, but I\Nthink I was able to reduce Yuka's burden\Nby being closer to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.72,0:45:46.72,ASS,,0,0,0,,I regret what I did in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.24,0:45:48.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.24,0:45:54.74,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka, you always say that you forget\Nabout the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.74,0:46:01.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,but I will never forget what you have\Ndone for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.24,0:46:06.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being our captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.24,0:46:08.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you. Have a good rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.24,0:46:09.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.24,0:46:11.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.24,0:46:14.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.74,0:46:18.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.68,0:46:32.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,(I like being alone)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.94,0:46:37.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,(I want to be with you forever, Yuka)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.44,0:46:39.68,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.68,0:46:42.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to be with you forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.24,0:46:43.48,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to be with you forever, Shikori.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.48,0:46:49.48,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking care of the time we\Nspend together.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.48,0:46:58.48,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yuka is taking a new step.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.48,0:47:13.48,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was able to create this wonderful\Nstage to stand on the second stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.03,0:47:17.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm very happy that I was able to see\Nyou off.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.03,0:47:33.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,The first day we talked was a casual\Nconversation, but now it's an\Nirreplaceable memory for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.03,0:47:39.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there was a moment like that,\Nso I think there is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.03,0:47:43.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,That moment is the most precious thing\Nin my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.54,0:47:46.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,It was a chance to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.54,0:47:49.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's a deep thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.54,0:47:53.27,ASS,,0,0,0,,When I think back,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.27,0:47:59.27,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was overflowing with memories of Yuka\NSona.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.27,0:48:10.27,ASS,,0,0,0,,At any moment, without wasting anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.27,0:48:16.27,ASS,,0,0,0,,we face each other with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.27,0:48:21.27,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Yuka Sona being by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.43,0:48:25.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,I think that's what Sakurazaka46 is like\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.13,0:48:31.43,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's not until the day I graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.33,0:48:36.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's finally the day I graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.93,0:48:38.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.93,0:48:45.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,This feeling of love has no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.43,0:48:51.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's something that will remain in\Neveryone's hearts forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.89,0:48:57.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please continue to spoil me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.89,0:48:58.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.89,0:49:01.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for the past 7 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.89,0:49:03.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.89,0:49:05.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please spoil me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.89,0:49:17.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm always supporting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.89,0:49:19.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm always having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.76,0:49:22.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.70,0:49:34.70,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.70,0:49:42.70,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.70,0:49:45.70,ASS,,0,0,0,,You wrote letters to me when you were\Nbusy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.70,0:49:50.70,ASS,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that you thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.70,0:49:57.70,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that I could be a captain who\Ncan help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.70,0:50:00.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I can be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.35,0:50:05.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm overflowing with gratitude for being\Nable to stand on such a wonderful stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.35,0:50:07.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.35,0:50:13.31,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please continue to support us with your\Nlove.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.31,0:50:22.31,ASS,,0,0,0,,(Applause)
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.31,0:50:26.31,ASS,,0,0,0,,And the next song will be the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.31,0:50:30.31,ASS,,0,0,0,,I would be happy if you could listen to\Nthis song for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.31,0:50:37.31,ASS,,0,0,0,,This song was written by Yasushi\NAkimoto, who is about to graduate\Ntomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.31,0:50:43.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm sad to say goodbye to everyone, but\NI'm going to the next stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.30,0:50:48.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'd like to sing a song for everyone\Nhere today.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.30,0:50:52.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.30,0:50:59.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, goodbye, goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.30,0:51:02.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm not sad
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.30,0:51:06.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Because we'll meet again someday
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.30,0:51:10.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Until that day
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.30,0:51:16.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, goodbye, goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.30,0:51:22.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yes, this place is here
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.30,0:51:27.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,A scene where everyone can see\Neverything
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.30,0:51:35.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,If you want something, you can get\Nanything
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.30,0:51:46.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I decided that I wouldn't be able to\Nforgive myself for being in such an\Nenvironment
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.30,0:51:52.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Where should I put what I have today?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.30,0:51:58.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I feel like I can live more freely
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.30,0:52:02.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, goodbye, goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.30,0:52:10.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I hope your heart will remain in one\Npiece while laughing and waving
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.30,0:52:16.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry for saying such a\Nselfish thing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.30,0:52:23.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,But I'm happy to see you off to become\Nan adult
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.30,0:52:25.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.30,0:52:26.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.30,0:52:35.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ah, the memories are empty
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.30,0:52:40.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Reflected from the depths of the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.30,0:52:48.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,New dreams are replaced by old dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.30,0:52:54.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's reassuring to have friends
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.30,0:52:59.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Even the timing of walking alone from\Nhere
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.30,0:53:05.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Even if I can't see the end of the dark\Nroad
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.30,0:53:13.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,My heart rises and believes in the light\Nof hope
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.30,0:53:20.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I pray, I pray, I pray for a happy\Nfuture
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.30,0:53:25.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,So that I won't regret today's farewell
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.30,0:53:30.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm sure, I'm sure, even if I'm afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.30,0:53:38.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'll just go forward with all my might\Nuntil that day
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.30,0:53:53.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me forever
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.30,0:54:01.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'll never forget you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.91,0:54:08.15,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Sakurazaka46"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.71,0:54:16.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,Today, I, Yuuka Suga, will be graduating\Nfrom Sakurazaka46.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.79,0:54:20.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,I received support from so many people,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.75,0:54:26.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,and I was able to run this far with the\Nsupport of my beloved members.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.24,0:54:37.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,So that I can meet everyone I love, I\Nwant to start a new journey from\Ntomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.24,0:54:42.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,I would be happy if you could wait until\NI can meet you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.24,0:54:44.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.24,0:54:48.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being with me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.87,0:54:51.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I've been fighting to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.87,0:54:56.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,There were sad things, but it was the\Nmost fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.87,0:54:59.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your support for 7 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.87,0:55:22.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being with me 7 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.87,0:55:26.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.87,0:55:30.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Next year I will be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.87,0:55:33.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.87,0:55:37.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.87,0:55:40.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.87,0:55:43.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.87,0:55:45.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for always being by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.87,0:55:49.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Sayonara, sayonara, sayonara
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.87,0:55:53.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be sad
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.87,0:55:59.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Until the day we meet again
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.87,0:56:05.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,See you, see you, see you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.87,0:56:08.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,With a smile on your face
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.87,0:56:13.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,May your heart's sadness remain
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.87,0:56:18.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry, for saying such\Nselfish things
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.87,0:56:26.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,But I'm strong enough to become an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.87,0:56:50.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Until the day we meet again
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.87,0:57:37.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Sayonara, sayonara, sayonara
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.87,0:57:48.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Sayonara, sayonara, sayonara"
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.87,0:58:18.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,If I'm with these members, I think I can\Novercome any difficulties
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.87,0:58:21.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I think I can move forward on any path
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.87,0:58:24.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to stand on this stage again
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.87,0:58:26.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to hold hands with the members
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.87,0:58:28.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to hold hands with the staff
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.87,0:58:31.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,And I want to hold hands with the\NBUDDIES
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.87,0:58:33.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to work together
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.87,0:58:38.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,From now on, SAKURAZAKA46 will continue\Nto climb the hill
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.87,0:58:40.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,To all the BUDDIES
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.87,0:58:46.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,From now on, we will continue to walk\Nwith SAKURAZAKA46
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.87,0:58:51.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please continue to support SAKURAZAKA46
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.87,0:58:53.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.87,0:59:04.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's all
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.87,0:59:07.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,We are SAKURAZAKA46
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.87,0:59:09.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.87,0:59:11.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.87,0:59:29.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.87,0:59:33.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please take a picture with us
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.87,0:59:40.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please take a lot of pictures\Nand post them on SNS
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.87,0:59:42.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.87,0:59:46.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.87,0:59:51.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.87,1:00:04.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.87,1:00:14.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I love you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.87,1:00:15.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.87,1:00:26.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I love you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.87,1:00:27.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.87,1:00:30.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
